{"word":"παιδεύω","slug":"παιδεύω","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b><el>παιδεύω</el></b> [<el><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:παῖς\">παῖς</a></el>] ‘exercise instructive discipline’<b><p class=\"pp3\"/>—<pp>a.</pp></b> <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ w.\">w.</a> focus on tutelage, <b>instruct <a href='B:510 7:22'>Ac 7:22</a>; <a href='B:510 22:3'>22:3</a>; offer guidance <a href='B:620 2:25'>2 Ti 2:25</a>; <a href='B:630 2:12'>Tit 2:12</a>.<p class=\"pp3\"/>—<pp>b.</pp></b> <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ w.\">w.</a> focus on corrective aspect, <b>discipline <a href='B:530 11:32'>1 Cor 11:32</a>; <a href='B:540 6:9'>2 Cor 6:9</a>; <a href='B:610 1:20'>1 Ti 1:20</a>; <a href='B:650 12:6'>Hb 12:6f</a>, 10; <a href='B:730 3:19'>Rv 3:19</a>.</b> In <b><a href='B:490 23:16'>Lk 23:16</a>, <a href='B:490 23:22'>22</a></b> <el>π.</el> connotes whipping or scourging as a ‘lesson’. <center id=\"nav_bottom\"> <a id=\"left_arrow\" href=\"S:παιδευτής\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> <a id=\"bottom_home\" href=\"S:#1.Table of Contents\">&emsp;&emsp;</a> <a id=\"right_arrow\" href=\"S:παιδιόθεν\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> </center> "}]}